Initial Surveyor 
:CONTENT:
}All participants in the Incident Command System(ICS) are Initial Surveyors.As you leave for the Incident Command Center or the Division Assembly Pointyou will check your close neighbors for any emergency situations.On you way to join the ICS you will make observation from the sidewalk for any damages, injuries, dangerous situations, or an all-clear signal.You will record each of your observations on the Damage Assessment Form.
:LIST:

